DIALOG_STORY2_GIRL1.zh: 你是谁？我怎么会晕倒在这里？

DIALOG_STORY2_GIRL2.en: You mean my hand and its red colour? Don't worry abaut that, i just got that from some powerful monster. Though ugly, its a lot stronger than my previous hand.
DIALOG_STORY2_GIRL2.zh: 你说这只红色的？它们没有问题，我从一个强大怪物的身体上获得了它们，虽然丑了点，但比我以前的强多了。

DIALOG_STORY2_GIRL3.en: You don't understand? Then, why are You here? Or perhaps you look for the same thing that i do?
DIALOG_STORY2_GIRL3.zh: 你不懂吗？那你为什么来这儿？难道你不是在寻找那件东西？

DIALOG_STORY2_GIRL4.zh: 真的吗？不过你必须先能够在岛上生存下去。捡起左边的那个肢体，它可以增强你的力量。

DIALOG_market_needmoney2.en: Something valuable for me, more limbs for you.

tips_2004.en: Many objects in the level can be hit, and occasionally drop some good things.
tips_2004.zh: 关卡中的很多物体都可以被击打，偶尔会掉落一些好东西。

DIALOG_market_needmoney1.en: If you want more of your precious lost limbs back. You'd better find something that i want.
DIALOG_market_needmoney1.zh: 如果你想以后我多给你带点儿遗失的肢体回来，你最好快点去找些我要的东西。

tips_2002.en: You can get the strength by attacking the enemies.
tips_2002.zh: 能量不足时，可以通过攻击敌人来获得补充。

tips_2003.en: Open the chest of the wild usually get rich rewards.
tips_2003.zh: 打开野外的宝箱通常会得到丰厚的奖励哦。

DIALOG_market_needmoney5.en: Find things i want and no one loses anything from my shelf for time of a quarter of an hour. You should feel honored.
DIALOG_market_needmoney5.zh: 找到这些我要的东西，还从来没有人丢掉的东西能在我的货架上待的时间超过一刻钟，或许你有这个荣幸。

skill_desc_CrowArmMain.zh: 召唤旋风攻击,连续攻击可使旋风变大变远。

tips_2008.en: Pay attention to your HP and supplies in the course of the combat, through timely replenishment of HP can avoid accidental death.
tips_2008.zh: 在战斗过程中时刻留意你的血量和补给品数量，通过及时补充血量能够避免意外死亡。

DIALOG_enhence_needmoney5.en: If you want to upgrade the 10 stage or more, you'll have to take risks to collect more material
DIALOG_enhence_needmoney5.zh: 如果你想再次提升10阶段以上的强化效果，就得再冒险去收集些更多的材料了，我可不想被外面的怪物吃掉~

DIALOG_enhence_needmoney4.en: The next step is to make my machine break through the limit of the number of times, to find these materials to prove my guess!
DIALOG_enhence_needmoney4.zh: 接下来就是让我的强化机突破强化次数限制了，快去找到这些材料证明我的猜想吧！

DIALOG_enhence_needmoney3.en: If you can find these things, perhaps to strengthen the effect of some of the more powerful.
DIALOG_enhence_needmoney3.zh: 如果能找到这些东西就好了，也许能让强化的效果更厉害一些。

DIALOG_enhence_needmoney1.en: I need some material to improve the machine to upgrade the times, but I can't deal with the monsters out there. Can you bring me back?
DIALOG_enhence_needmoney1.zh: 我需要些材料改进强化机来升级强化次数，但我对付不了外面那些怪物，你能帮我带些回来吗？

DIALOG_69.en: Remember to come to me next time.

DIALOG_60.en: In all stories, anyone like you with these broken equipments can't live through two sets.

DIALOG_62.en: Not 998 golds, not 98 golds, only 20 golds, you can take the treasure with you.
DIALOG_62.zh: 不要998，不要98，只要20金币，神兵利器带回家，怎么样？

DIALOG_64.en: There was one guy as generous as you, I don't know what became of him.
DIALOG_64.zh: 之前有个人也像你一样慷慨，不知道他现在怎么样了……

DIALOG_65.en: Now, you look like a master.

DIALOG_66.en: Do I look like a pie uncle?
DIALOG_66.zh: 我像是烙馅饼的大叔吗？

DIALOG_67.zh: 你遇见了警察吗？路途艰辛，何不给我20金币让我好好陪陪你？
